   "source": [
    "# Question Generation Examples\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook shows how to generate questions using the current codebase. By default it uses the **local stub provider** (no API keys needed). Set `PROVIDER`/`MODEL` below and add keys in `.env` if you want OpenAI/Yandex.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys, os\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "from pprint import pprint\n",
    "\n",
    "project_root = Path(__file__).parent.parent.parent\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, str(project_root))\n",
    "\n+    "from app.core.exam_builder import generate_question\n",
    "\n",
    "# Configure provider/model\n",
    "PROVIDER = os.getenv(\"NOTEBOOK_PROVIDER\", \"local\")  # set to \"openai\" or \"yandex\" if keys provided\n",
    "MODEL = os.getenv(\"NOTEBOOK_MODEL\")  # optional\n",
    "\n",
    "SNIPPET = \"\"\"\n",
    "## Heart Failure\n",
    "Heart failure is a chronic condition where the heart cannot pump enough blood to meet the body's needs.\n",
    "Typical symptoms include dyspnea, fatigue, and peripheral edema. Treatment often involves ACE inhibitors,\n",
    "beta-blockers, diuretics, and lifestyle modifications.\n",
    "\"\"\"\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Single-choice question in Russian\n",
    "q_single = generate_question(\n",
    "    SNIPPET,\n",
    "    question_type=\"single_choice\",\n",
    "    difficulty=\"medium\",\n",
    "    provider=PROVIDER,\n",
    "    model_name=MODEL,\n",
    "    language=\"ru\"\n",
    ")\n",
    "pprint(q_single)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
